1. Dashboard

Challenges & Solutions

Challenge 1: Complex Workflow Simplification

AI model training involves complex parameters and settings that could overwhelm users.

Solution:

  • â€¢ Implemented a progressive disclosure pattern
  • â€¢ Created guided workflows with clear progress indicators
  • â€¢ Provided sensible defaults with advanced options available

Challenge 2: Real-time Feedback

Users need immediate feedback during voice interactions and model training.

Solution:

  • â€¢ Implemented real-time visual feedback for voice input
  • â€¢ Added progress indicators for long-running operations
  • â€¢ Used WebSockets for live updates
